Localization.Name: Variable Service Shoes
Localization.Description: Code Blue Apparel's Variable Service Shoes are constructed from a rigid rubber-carbon splice that help provide protection from physical impacts or piercings. The exterior is sprayed with artileather for a professional finish and offers maximum ease-of-cleaning.
